# Keep build noise out of the image.
#
# NOTE: this file must be named `.dockerignore` (WITH the leading dot). The copy in
# the repo was named `dockerignore`, so Docker never read it and every build has been
# shipping whatever else happened to be in the folder. Harmless while the folder is
# clean, but it is doing nothing.
#
# Rename on save:  wrangler-worker/.dockerignore

# R noise
.Rhistory
.RData
.Rproj.user/
.Renviron

# Local fit artifacts. `disposition` (or disposition.exe) is the compiled Stan binary:
# it MUST NOT be copied in, because the Dockerfile compiles the model itself and a
# stale binary from another architecture would either be ignored or break the build.
disposition
disposition.exe
disposition_posteriors.csv
*.csv

# Docs
README*.md
